# Production split deploy: full API base ending in /api (axios adds resource paths)
# Example: VITE_API_URL=https://your-api.example.com/api
#
# Combined deploy (API serves client/dist): leave unset so the app uses same-origin /api/
#
# Local dev: leave unset to use Vite proxy (vite.config.js) → http://localhost:5000
